title: handbook of mold tool and die welding
description: "Handbook of Mold, Tool and Die Repair Welding is a great book for anyone who wants to become or is beginning a career as a tool welder. Experienced tool welders are sure to come away with some new ideas, and could certainly use the book as a reference or training tool. Toolmakers who work with welders will gain a more thorough understanding of the problems welders face..." (From a review in Injection Molding Magazine by Rocky Huber, Ivanhoe Tool & Die Company).
